    "TimeDiff": "- \n0.33 hrs",
    "Notes": "<p data-start=\"164\" data-end=\"451\">We received a security alert indicating that an unencrypted password file exists on system <strong data-start=\"272\" data-end=\"283\">AAOC-28</strong> at the following path:<br data-start=\"306\" data-end=\"309\" /><code data-start=\"309\" data-end=\"450\">C:\\Users\\cordero.AAOC\\Apartment Association of Orange County\\Secure - Documents\\_ACCOUNTING\\_PASSWORDS\\Accounting Passwords 12-18-2023.xlsx</code>.</p><p data-start=\"453\" data-end=\"606\">This file contains passwords and is stored in an unencrypted state, posing a significant security risk. Such files are vulnerable to unauthorized access.</p><p data-start=\"608\" data-end=\"626\"><strong data-start=\"608\" data-end=\"626\">Actions Taken:</strong></p><ol data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"990\"><li data-section-id=\"5qtbt8\" data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"692\"><p data-start=\"630\" data-end=\"692\">The file path was confirmed and flagged as a security concern.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"1jn5uoo\" data-start=\"693\" data-end=\"990\"><p data-start=\"696\" data-end=\"756\">We advised <strong data-start=\"707\" data-end=\"718\">Cordero</strong> to take one of the following actions:</p><ul data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"990\"><li data-section-id=\"32qpn\" data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"901\"><p data-start=\"762\" data-end=\"901\"><strong data-start=\"762\" data-end=\"782\">Encrypt the file</strong> with a strong password via <strong data-start=\"810\" data-end=\"843\">File &gt; Protect Using Password</strong> or <strong data-start=\"847\" data-end=\"900\">Tools &gt; Protect &gt; Encrypt &gt; Encrypt with Password</strong>.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"rt92a8\" data-start=\"905\" data-end=\"990\"><p data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"990\">If the file is no longer needed, <strong data-start=\"940\" data-end=\"950\">delete</strong> it to prevent potential security risks.</p></li></ul></li></ol><p data-start=\"992\" data-end=\"1007\"><strong data-start=\"992\" data-end=\"1007\">Next Steps:</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1008\" data-end=\"1098\"><li data-section-id=\"1e93vu7\" data-start=\"1008\" data-end=\"1098\"><p data-start=\"1010\" data-end=\"1098\">Follow-up with Cordero to ensure encryption is applied, or confirm deletion of the file.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1178\"><strong data-start=\"1100\" data-end=\"1111\">Status:</strong> Awaiting confirmation from Cordero on encryption or file deletion.</p>",
